{
  "stem": "19921.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 98.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was about an hour and a half lecture which went very well through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was invited also by them privately and before when they have more time to come and to be in their living room, in their quarters, and already talk soldier to soldier.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I would take them up on that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We will do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But that strictly was talk about liberation concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I-- that's the only thing which I do, what I saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I cannot say that I was in the camp, because I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Even so, I, you know, lost the whole family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But nevertheless, it is not very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it's very painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Believe it not, after so many years, it's very painful to talk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I get tremendous headaches after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But it's worth it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "To inform people, it's worth it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I really don't know how long we have on this earth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And as long as we can continue, lot of people would show the same thing which I did unfortunately didn't make it through the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we have to speak for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And as far as the medals from the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Yes, I received medals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Some in Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But mostly, I left everything there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I just take the documentation which I have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I took with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was afraid to transport medals from Poland to Germany, first of all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And if my wife would have known that I took the documents, she would have killed me on the spot because, you know, it-- it was not smart.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But I couldn't part with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So after the Polish regime, the communist regime, fell there, I started to write a letter to the consulate here in New York City.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And documented.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
